description:
EndcProfile: Table storing eNodeB  New Radio (NR) End-to-End Connection (Endc) profile configurations.

dateTime: Timestamp of the profile record.
Area_Name: Geographic area associated with the profile.
CellId: Unique identifier for the cell.
Id2: Redundant cell identifier.
Id3:  Generic identifier, possibly related to service type.
vsDataType:  Data type identifier, specifying this is an Endc profile.
vsDataFormatVersion:  Version of the data format used.
EndcProfile.userLabel: User-friendly label for the profile.
EndcProfile.meNbS1TermReqArpLev:  ARPU level for ME NB S1 termination requests.
EndcProfile.endcProfileId: Unique identifier for the Endc profile.
EndcProfile.reservedBy:  String containing information specifying  the reservation context of the profile.
EndcProfile.splitNotAllowedUeArpLev: ARPU level for which UE splitting is not allowed.
